entries.journal_entry_completion_summary: You have eliminated Trins Evnar and all but one of his contacts within the Chirq Council. Almost done.
entries.journal_entry_description: It's time for you to take the place of Trins Evnar. First, of course, you'll have to eliminate Trins Evnar. You'll also need to eliminate anyone within the Chirq Council who directly knew Trins.
entries.journal_entry_title: The Chirq Council: Assumed Identity - Part One
entries.task01_journal_entry_description: Search Trins Evnar's house for any information on his Chirq Council contacts.
entries.task02_journal_entry_description: Return to Captain Baize and await further instructions.
entries.task03_journal_entry_description: Trins Evnar had four direct points of contact within the Chirq Council. The first two, Genovin Jasha and Seyda Shae, have a base outside of town. Start by eliminating them.
entries.task04_journal_entry_description: Trins' next contact is Jade McDonagh. She has a small junk business in town. Take her out.
entries.task08_journal_entry_description: Destroy the mainframe at Genovin and Seyda's base.
entries.task09_item_name: You have downloaded all data from Trins Evnar's datapad
entries.task09_journal_entry_description: Access Trins Evnar's personal datapad and download all data stored within it.
entries.task10_item_name: You have downloaded data on all recent incoming and outgoing communication
entries.task10_journal_entry_description: Access Trins Evnar's answering service and download data on recent incoming and outgoing communication.
entries.task11_item_name: You have downloaded all data from Trins Evnar's data terminal
entries.task11_journal_entry_description: Access Trins Evnar's data terminal and download all data stored within it.
